test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x766b6ac8f140>([42])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x766b6ac8f140> = [[1, 42], [1, 42, 1], [42], [42, 1], [1, 42], [1, 42, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1 == 42
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
